香港（第五）港、廣州港（第七）、青島港（第八）和天津港（第十）。"},{"pid":"c223b050bda673300fd353a8212831667d6cfefd","tid":188932,"uid":103795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全世界四百幾個商業港<br />\n貨櫃吞吐量香港排第五<br />\n點解會係夕陽?</blockquote><br />\n好多人成日話物流乞食乜乜77<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔明但又唔識駁"},{"pid":"3070dcfeac152f005c12d776bd6f3d296c11e3bb","tid":188932,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:07:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4803817eddef89a1f8aefc0883211f5614a300ef","tid":188932,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>全世界四百幾個商業港<br />\n貨櫃吞吐量香港排第五<br />\n點解會係夕陽?</blockquote><br />\n好多人成日話物流乞食乜乜77<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔明但又唔識駁</blockquote><br />\n屌搵到錢果D唔通同你講咩  <br />\n你又唔係佢地親戚 洗撚同你講.......<br />\n有時間佢地搵多D錢好過啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識人真係中五畢業都有五皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f12d46f1f1d9072b27e6e520dc269e0aed68fe6","tid":188932,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:14:46.000Z","msg":"因為呀豬呀狗都整部車又搞物流，啲公司又搞外判，抄牌又越黎越多"},{"pid":"a8371cb08139eb7addea1818aad34a7cee59c2eb","tid":188932,"uid":60529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:15:54.000Z","msg":"航運的確收緊皮 依家d 大陸廠執哂 香港冇野走<br />\n南亞d 廠出貨除非去美國否則唔洗經香港"},{"pid":"02d9922368480f124d89e17657e32f83fb32f92c","tid":188932,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"快d叫埋d it手足轉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d438b88ea90fe9f2d1222bcf40da7f0bb2243a4","tid":188932,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:18:06.000Z","msg":"你睇下葵涌碼頭個吞吐量先,雖然比唔上以前咁架勢,但都係香港GDP最重要的部份<br />\n<br />\n中國國力愈差香港個物流業就愈好"},{"pid":"47a405a4b66ea0